  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2991_2",
    "text": "娃（塑） 现代 陕西",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.35964310226492796,
      0.189453125,
      0.5774422328986502,
      0.205078125
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2991",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2991_3",
    "text": "每逢节庆，们便把 食做成面花，为节日增添光 彩。这个面花物，身披无数 鲜花，托彩凤，神采奕奕， 光彩照人。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3568977350720659,
      0.20572916666666666,
      0.5994051704415465,
      0.279296875
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2991",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2991_4",
    "text": "兔爷（泥塑） 现代 北京",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.03935026309768932,
      0.3873697916666667,
      0.2571493937314116,
      0.40234375
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2991",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2991_0",
    "text": "兔爷是北京中秋节民 俗的标志之一，是一种人身兔 的泥玩具。这种别具匠的 造型，表现出北京的浪漫心 性和乐观幽默的性格。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.036604895904827274,
      0.4036458333333333,
      0.2809425760695493,
      0.4765625
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2991",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2991_5",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "picture",
    "bbox": [
